THEATRE LIBRARIANSHIP. OCCASIONAL PUBLICATION SERIES NUMBER TEN.
     
DEVELOPED TO SHED LIGHT ON UK THEATRE LIBRARIANSHIP, THIS STUDY DEFINES
THEATRE LIBRARIES, ILLUSTRATES THE KIND OF WORK CARRIED OUT IN THEATRE
LIBRARIES AND COLLECTIONS, REVIEWS FUNCTIONAL PROBLEM AREAS, AND ADVOCATES
BETTER ORGANISATION, FINANCING, AND STAFFING FOR THESE UNIQUE INSTITUTIONS.
REPORT NOT AVAILABLE FROM NTIS.
